extends layout

block content
  .landing-wrap
    h1 WCB Form Replication — Assignment 2
    p.sub
      | Server-rendered with Pug. Every field is populated from a simulated
      | backend record — there is no data entry on screen. Use the toolbar
      | on each form to switch between two different backend records and
      | to print a standard A4 PDF.

    a.card(href="/worker-progress?sample=A")
      .title Worker Progress Report →
      .desc 3-page form · return-to-work & recovery details · driven entirely by backend data

    a.card(href="/medical-travel?sample=A")
      .title Medical & Travel Expense Request →
      .desc 2-page form · 6 expense tables rendered from one reusable mixin · row counts vary by record
